name: The Dawning of a New Day
description: This image, "The Dawning of a New Day" was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence (AI). The concept behind this image reflects one's hope for a new day of liberty, justice, and equality for all. The process for creating this image included using a text prompt, algorithms, and artificial intelligence. The Snowpixel App was used in this process of creating this unique image. The image will be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewer.
